# delegate

**Instance Property**

The outline view’s delegate.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor weak var delegate: (any NSOutlineViewDelegate)? { get set }
```

## Discussion

The delegate must conform to the [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSOutlineViewDelegate] protocol. Note that in versions of macOS prior to v10.12, the table view did not retain the delegate in a managed memory environment.
